response.overview: June 27th, 2008 :: Ring Of Honor presents Battle for Supremacy from the Montgomery County Fairgrounds in Dayton, Ohio.  Matches include:  • Title Unification Match ROH World Champion Nigel McGuinness vs NWA World Champion Adam Pierce  • Bryan Danielson vs Erick Stevens  • No Disqualification Match Austin Aries vs Necro Butcher  • The Age of the Fall (Jimmy Jacobs & Joey Matthews) vs Kevin Steen & El Generico  • Chris Hero vs Roderick Strong  • Brent Albright vs Claudio Castagnoli vs Jay Briscoe  • Tyler Black vs Delirious  • Tank Toland & Shane Hagadorn vs Silas Young & Mitch Franklin
response.title: ROH: Battle For Supremacy
